e us land segment operates its drilling business primarily in oklahoma california texas wyoming colorado louisiana mississippi pennsylvania ohio utah new mexico montana north dakota west virginia and nevada the offshore segment conducts its business in the gulf of mexico and equatorial guinea the international land segment operates in six international locations including ecuador colombia argentina bahrain united arab emirates and mozambique the company was founded by walter helmerich ii and william payne in  and is headquartered in tulsa ok expand key people helmerich  payne inc board of directors nametitle current board membership hans c helmerich  chairman the northwestern mutual life insurance co helmerich  payne international drilling co atwood oceanics inc cimarex energy co helmerich  payne inc john w lindsay  president chief executive officer  director helmerich  payne inc tulsa area united way josé ramón mas  director helmerich  payne inc kevin g cramton director helmerich  payne inc thomas a petrie  independent director petrie partners llc helmerich  payne inc the denver art museum paula a marshallchapman  independent director american fidelity corp founders fund inc helmerich  payne inc edward barry rust  independent director state farm associates funds trusts state farm insurance cos illinois wesleyan university americas promise alliance the conference board inc caterpillar inc helmerich  payne inc sp global inc state farm vp management corp state farm mutual automobile insurance co state farm mutual fund trust state farm variable product trust randy a foutch  independent director laredo petroleum inc the catholic foundation of eastern oklahoma inc university of tulsa leadership oklahoma the gilcrease museum national board helmerich  payne inc laredo petroleum llc john d zeglis  independent director helmerich  payne inc the culver educational foundation george washington university council for aid to education united negro college fund inc amx corp state 