 driller helmerich  payne after  years of service he continued on as chairman of the board helmerich turned the reins over to john lindsay marking the first time a nonfamily member has led the company since its founding nearly a century ago lindsay started working for hp as an oilfield roughneck in  he has been president since  from a very young age helmerich cultivated an admiration for the company his grandfather founded employing the lessons he learned in his early days hans elevated hp from a company with a mn market cap to a bn company that is a leader in us shale plays read what it takes to be number one the vision  legacy of hans helmerich oilpro unlike this like  send share facebook linkedin twitter google × share to usual suspects more preview message send oilpro sponsors site map oilpro is the professional network built for the oil and gas industry connect with colleagues keep up with industry trends and discover how oilpro can increase your industry influence learn more and join us today oilpro copyright  hp hans c helmerich insider trades for helmerich  payne inc bulletin investor alert new york markets open in market snapshot analyst ratings expand keep open close expand keep open close expand keep open close expand keep open close expand keep open close helmerich  payne inc nyse hp go set alerts find a broker join td ameritrade market index overview profile news charts financials historical quotes analyst estimates options sec filings insiders marketstatecountryus helmerich  payne inc after hours  quotes are delayed by  min jul    pm hp quoteszigmancomposite   change   volume volume  quotes are delayed by  min quoteszigmancomposite previous close     change   day low day high    week low  week high   insider activity individual hans c helmerich mr hans c helmerich is independent director at cimarex energy co independent director at atwood oceanics inc chairman at helmerich  payne inc and president chief executive officer  director at helmerich  payne i